frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature construction workers decorating a giant ice cream cone. The workers, dressed in orange uniforms and yellow helmets, are using ladders and a scissor lift to place colorful sprinkles on the creamy swirl. The setting is playful and imaginative, blending elements of construction with a dessert theme.
frames.description: The scene is set in a surreal world where tiny construction workers are tasked with decorating a massive ice cream cone. The workers are actively climbing ladders, operating a scissor lift, and placing sprinkles, creating a lively and humorous atmosphere.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature construction workers on a cup of cappuccino, treating the frothy surface as a construction site. The workers, equipped with tools and safety gear, appear to be shaping the foam and cocoa powder. The background is filled with coffee beans, enhancing the playful coffee-themed setting.
frames.description: The image presents a creative and imaginative scene where tiny construction workers are engaged in activities on a cup of cappuccino. The setting is designed to resemble a construction site, with coffee beans scattered around, adding to the thematic atmosphere.
